OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Simeon
OL,4,CMayou
OL,6,FSimeon Mayoy, Age: 99, Royal Navy
OL,7,FPatrol Service
OL,9,FInterviewed 20 February 2024
OL,11,FDied 28 December 2024
OL,13,FOn board HMS Fusilier on D-Day, Mr
OL,14,FMayou was a radar operator who'd
OL,15,Fpreviously been escorting Atlantic
OL,16,Fconvoys.
OL,18,FThe ship was a heavily-armed naval
OL,19,Ftrawler and told to head to the
OL,20,FChannel ports.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
